{
  "stem": "1183.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There was a dividing line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was the entrance and we were there, and The gypsies were on the other side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So as punishment, I had to sit in between them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So then I came back to the own one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And if there was water, the SS or the women or men just threw the water into the cattle car, but didn't give us to drink.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So the women, in desperation, started to drink their own urine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You had to have something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I still remember having it in my hand and then the train made a sudden movement.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It fell out of my hand, and I never drank it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also vividly remember that I had-- how do you say it?-- delusions, or I went out of it, because I know exactly feeling.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there, but I was walking in a-- like your conscious does that, was walking in a big, big room, just wandering around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still remember that feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although, because you know, we were so tightly packed together and that's why you escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that feeling I remembered very much, walking in a big, big, big room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, well-- So finally, we somewhere ended.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They stopped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they opened the doors and we could get out, and then had some water and we are outside.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, in another place-- continued our travel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Another place, we were let out on a grassy area more or less, in a bush.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There we were able to wash a little bit and to wander around too, although, we had to be careful, for-- because there was still air raids and so on going on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was Bendorf.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were also close by a town in East Germany, still from Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
